data.meta_description: All Obituaries - Pippin Funeral Home offers a variety of funeral services, from traditional funerals to competitively priced cremations, serving Camden-Wyoming, DE and the surrounding communities. We also offer funeral pre-planning and carry a wide selection of caskets, vaults, urns and burial containers.

Barbara Barnhart Lancaster, PA, formerly of Dover, DE

Barbara Barnhart, 103, formerly of Dover, passed away August 8, 2024, at her residence in Lancaster, PA. She was born in Grantsville, MD on June 2, 1921, to Allen and Alma (Miller) Maust. In 1946 she moved to Dover, DE to teach school. In 1957 she married James Barnhart who passed away in 1972.
